Installation Script
https://get.docker.com/

curl -fsSL get.docker.com -o get-docker.sh
sh get-docker.sh
To run the containers without sudo access, add the current user to docker group
usermod -aG docker user-name
docker version { only client is up, we need to start the daemon}
sudo systemctl start docker
docker version
docker info
Once docker is up and running, test the installation by running the simple Docker image
docker images (or) docker image ls
docker ps (or) docker container ls
